Featured opportunities (snapshot)

  • Argentina — Lithium salar JV. Brine field with evaporation ponds & camp on site; adjacent to Tier-1 operator. Transaction: JV or asset sale (LOI required).

Our process

  1. Sourcing & screening (KYC, mandate, ownership check)
  2. Technical & legal due diligence (NI 43-101 / JORC-style evidence where available)
  3. Transaction design (JV, earn-in, asset sale, M&A)
  4. Execution & governance (timelines, covenants, reporting)

Compliance & trust

We operate with strict anti-fraud and AML standards. No upfront fees; NDAs/NCNDAs and LOIs required to exchange sensitive data.

Ports for energy deals (when applicable): Rotterdam, Fujairah, Houston. Full documentation upon buyer validation.
